Her attire is an intricate fusion of a magical girl idol and a disciplined knight. For her upper body, she wears a fitted, dark obsidian-colored bodice with a sharp, geometric "V" neckline, overlaid with golden filigree that traces the contours of her torso. This is layered over a vibrant orange and red under-piece. Her sleeves are detached, starting at the mid-bicep with ruffled, translucent orange fabric tipped in gold, leading down to sleek, silver and white vambraces on her forearms that provide a touch of armored protection. The lower body features a multi-layered, short "tutu" style skirt that mimics the petals of a flower or the spread of a flame, consisting of tiers of yellow, orange, and red translucent fabric with scalloped, golden-trimmed edges. Underneath, she wears opaque white thigh-high stockings that emphasize her slender yet athletic physique, finished with elegant white high-heeled shoes featuring gold accents and sharp, pointed toes.

