The background depicts a grand, theatrical stage set for a "9th Happy Birthday" celebration. The floor is a polished, circular platform with glowing, runic patterns etched into the glass-like surface, reflecting the bright spotlights from above. Behind her, a massive, tiered golden arch rises like a stylized sunburst, decorated with silhouettes of dancing figures and musical notations. To her left, a collection of oversized, colorful gift boxes in shades of purple, green, and blue are stacked, accompanied by a small, grumpy-looking plush toy of a white-haired character. To her right stands a giant, three-tiered chocolate cake topped with a lit "9th" candle and chocolate-filled wafers. The entire scene is framed by clusters of floating balloons in purple, pink, and gold, while the silhouettes of a cheering crowd holding glowing blue and pink light sticks can be seen in the foreground, creating an atmosphere of high-energy performance and festive triumph.






