Her attire is a sophisticated blend of futuristic "magitech" armor and sleek, form-fitting fabric. On her upper body, she wears a white and silver bodice featuring intricate red filigree and a glowing orange star-shaped core at the center of her chest, which acts as the focal point of her power. Her shoulders are protected by flared, dark crimson pauldrons with gold trim, which transition into sleek, armored sleeves. These sleeves do not fully cover her arms, leaving sections of her upper arms exposed before connecting to white-and-gold gauntlets that protect her forearms and hands. The lower half of her outfit consists of a short, layered white skirt with sharp, petal-like edges trimmed in gold and crimson. Beneath this, she wears dark, iridescent navy or black leggings that provide a seamless, aerodynamic silhouette, ending in pointed, armored boots that match the aesthetic of her gauntlets. Floating around her waist and hips are several golden, crystalline shards that act as both decorative accessories and reactive armor pieces.

