The background depicts a chaotic, breathtaking cosmic battlefield set within a deep-space nebula. The atmosphere is thick with swirling clouds of violet, magenta, and deep indigo gas, illuminated by distant stars and the destructive glow of celestial combat. Massive, dark-textured geometric structures, resembling ruined spacecraft or ancient alien monoliths, float weightlessly in the periphery, some shattered into jagged asteroids. Traces of high-speed energy trails zigzag through the void, suggesting a large-scale aerial dogfight occurring in the distance. The lighting is dramatic and high-contrast, with the character being back-lit by a blindingly bright light source—possibly a dying star or a warp gate—which casts long, sharp shadows and makes the translucent crystalline elements of her armor glow with an internal radiance. She stands as the calm, lethal center of this interstellar storm, a god-like figure traversing the "Sundering" of the universe itself.






