Her outfit is an intricate fusion of futuristic "tech-wear" and magical girl aesthetics. On her upper body, she wears a form-fitting dark indigo leotard adorned with a glowing, butterfly-shaped crest on the chest that transitions through shades of neon pink, yellow, and violet. This torso piece is framed by jagged, crystalline shoulder pauldrons in a deep purple-to-black gradient, with neon green star-shaped motifs embedded within them. Her arms are partially covered by detached sleeves and sleek bracers that end in sharp, wing-like protrusions at the elbows. From the side and back, one can see a complex mechanical harness featuring glowing circular thrusters—one magenta and one emerald green—which likely provide her with flight or high-speed propulsion. Below, she wears iridescent, patterned leggings that shimmer with a golden honeycomb texture under the light, ending in sharp, high-tech greaves and boots that mimic the pointed, crystalline aesthetic of her weaponry.

